<p><strong>Project:</strong> EmployeeApp.Api&nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Target Framework:</strong> .NET 10&nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Cache Server:</strong> Microsoft Garnet (RESP/Redis-protocol compatible)&nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Client Library:</strong> Microsoft.Extensions.Caching.StackExchangeRedis</p>

