<h2>15. Summary</h2>
<p>
By running Microsoft Garnet locally as a .NET global tool and wiring it into ASP.NET Core's standard
<code>IDistributedCache</code> abstraction via <code>Microsoft.Extensions.Caching.StackExchangeRedis</code>, the
employee list served by <code>EmployeeService.GetAllAsync()</code> is cached for a configurable window and
automatically invalidated on create, update, and delete &mdash; reducing load on SQL Server while keeping the data
consistent, following the same configuration-driven pattern already established for RabbitMQ in this project.
</p>

